        "TileImage": "$($repository db51f79b-578b-470b-8bf8-bed82e2e250e).Image",
        "Description": "47, you have a new contract. A radical activist group has hired you to eliminate 5 servants of the bourgeoisie. These 5 have been known to sacrifice the wellbeing and stability of their fellows to further their own standing and follow the corrupt leadership of the rich with no regards for common decency. Eliminate these sychophants to send a clear message: capitalism shall burn, and anybdy who shields it will burn with it.\r\rGood hunting, comrade 47.",
